{"type": "article", "id": 42767, "title": "Viktor&Rolf 走了一场很特别的秀，以及，Dior 的大展值得一看 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-07-07T03:05:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 9472, "name": "Colette"}, {"id": 42136, "name": "巴黎高定秀"}, {"id": 1530, "name": "Lanvin"}, {"id": 10699, "name": "L Brands"}, {"id": 42137, "name": "英国服装市场"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170707105310UWnV3TcFIl8tK1M5.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://fashionunited.uk/news/business/uk-clothing-market-to-reach-51-2-billion-pounds-by-2022/2017070625093\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>英国服装市场有望在五年内增长 16.6%，达到 512 亿英镑 </strong></a>| 据英国媒体报道，受英国退欧影响，英镑疲软导致进口成本增加，服装将是英国第三个增长最快的部门，本土服装市场将在 2022 年之前达到 512 亿英镑。男装将是增长最快的类别之一，预计增长 21.2%，在英国的男装增长将由时尚影响力增加驱动。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/l-brands-victorias-secret-sixth-month-of-sales-declines-10940547/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>维多利亚的秘密母公司业绩继续下滑</strong></a> | 维多利亚的秘密母公司 L Brands 集团发布半年财报，今年前 6 个月销售额连续下滑，6 月净销售额为 12 亿美元，较上年同期也减少了 6%，股价下跌了 13.4%。该公司称，去年撤掉泳装和大部分产品的决定是今年业绩下滑的主要原因。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/business-features/bouchra-jarrar-said-leaving-lanvin-10940488/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Lanvin 设计总监离职</strong></a> | 日前，Bouchra Jarrar 宣布将在 2018 年春夏系列发布之前离职。Bouchra Jarrar 于 2016 年三月加入 Lanvin，仅为该品牌推出了两个系列。据称离职原因是与 Lanvin 首席执行官 Michele Huiban 不和。另有消息表示，目前 Lanvin 的 300 名员工非常不安，或将面临裁员危险。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/puma-marine-pack\" rel=\"nofollow\">PUMA 又一次以日本浮世绘为主题推出球鞋，以海浪图绘向日本的“海之日”致敬</a>。</p><p>这次的海洋系列球鞋分别有 Disc Blaze、Easy Rider 及 Clyde 三个经典鞋款，另外还有夹克衫和 T 恤等单品，将于 7 月 13 日登陆 PUMA 的指定零售店。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104444zNyHndmGqjKi7gLU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104444A6URj5i2pMYhTCx8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104444xRyki8sPlOzt4oFA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104442uGLfalPUVjJBy5qK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104443AfPCYNmFaEoJerHO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104444eZWJSpv0TAczRriL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104444LxoD9kVTHKIUBbZ7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707071044434mUCcbwtv0lWfMPd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/rmk-x-roaringwild-workwear\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本街头品牌 ROARINGWILD，联手日式烧酒屋 RUMAKU</a>，推出了一套专属员工制服，包括衬衫、马甲、围裙等，都根据调酒师的工作习惯进行了特殊剪裁和设计。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104525vgzbOMdqCpVw2NRJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104525qzJv3BIGcrCQLsko.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104525z21ZHO0VGcCSUnvr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104524pmAr16cDzHqGg0Ra.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104524ZGu7VdY9MzUjvLB5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104524ej1ofSJPXlFdc2xy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104524EkAgQFP6STL1H0O9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104524bAkzsJmKRPFV0rMq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707071045330EiYD8TWKzAd7NX6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>最近，<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/hm-studio-colette-collaboration-tease\" rel=\"nofollow\">巴黎 colette 放出消息，要与 H&amp;M 旗下的高端支线 H&amp;M Studio 合作打造联名系列。</a>这也将是 H&amp;M 首次与其它零售商展开合作，目前仅率先曝光了几件单品。该系列将于 8 月 21 日在 colette 官方网站发售，然后于 9 月 14 日登陆 H&amp;M 门店。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104611XuxtLgpeWKVBvlUk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707071046089wqoNVg3MxtJFLvI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104608ciaXtZfWRQMsJhHY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.775982\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>巴黎高定秀上，以高定起家的设计师品牌 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/runway-fashion/viktor-rolf-fall-2017-couture/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Viktor&amp;Rolf 带来了一场很特别的秀</a>。 </p><p>模特儿们身巨型蝴蝶结、夸张的荷叶边，戴着大头娃娃头套走上了天台。设计师 Rolf Snoeren 觉得，当下的现实是很奇怪的，那为何不展现超现实的一面？</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707071046456qPtXCOkTazgZBdU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017070710464642pdYgFDyqt0MxbN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104646dqrEWgFbwXCsGZc3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104646E56UPWJVZ4jqvh93.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104646XT3lgAQzyaRZx8e9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707071046468x2JiEXmZRsragqH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104646lZHJ5LYgiGuR2IVM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104647eVCudY30IElcnrtb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104644VMUSLsep6dIZEJh9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707071046477Jt2TxeuDqGON45E.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104644uTR8OnPs0StC1NbE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104647UVRcEeI9jqOsN6lQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104647p9xkYLe1r5EfP3t7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104647mEQLikHRO8Uu4XyF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104648Gv6BOIm8nkFH173q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104645jHzXmedS5pTiKYgn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104645PdFry3kEufXvDIG6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104645Rkac3yPKmVulojB0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104644b4DBV3MGPhovHyIq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-events/dior-christian-dior-designer-of-dreams-exhibition/\" rel=\"nofollow\">七月高定秀期间，Dior 在巴黎装饰艺术博物馆举办了一场名为《Christian Dior, Designer of Dreams.》的大型展览。 </a></p><p>展览共展出 300 多套由 1947 年至今的 Dior 高级定制礼服，工作室样衣、插图、手稿、照片和笔记等。这可能是今年最值得一看的时尚展览，它将一直持续至明年 1 月 7 日。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104825XeHGzljVDTYiFsgZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104817jXun0IYS5RQcAJde.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104817pm0LHGlf5hZFzRgX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104817XNdO3rYo7amILfCP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104818dLamyrXE3PhDuKF5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104818sehnpFCcJ5B6jrIX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104819a8Uugir7HKxmAkW0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104819Woxa8jHzC2JtnTvS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104819sWFSoayjYruptOCx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707071048244bJC6NSuH0fDjXT3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104824exdU4wzGjXPgt0f3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104824C0hFrwBZbJHEmaqY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104824RXiHQkDqUdfrTwB4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170707104824azlRv4hUeDQKOIjT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-events/dior-christian-dior-designer-of-dreams-exhibition/\" rel=\"nofollow\">popbee</a></p>"}